for(s in 1:1000)
{
  ## -- update covariances  
  E<-Y-outer(a,b,"+")
  iPsi<-rwish(  solve( E%*%iSigma%*%t(E) + diag(n) ) , p+n+1 )
  iSigma<-rwish(  solve( t(E)%*%iPsi%*%E + diag(p) ) , n+p+1 )

  ## -- update mean parameters 
  Vab<-solve(  t(X)%*%(iSigma %x% iPsi)%*%X  + diag(n+p) )
  eab<-Vab%*% t(X)%*%(iSigma %x% iPsi)%*%c(Y)
  ab<- eab + mhalf(Vab)%*%rnorm(n+p)
  a<-ab[1:n]
  b<-ab[n+1:p]

  ## -- summarize output 
  EPsi<-EPsi+solve(iPsi)
  ESigma<-ESigma+solve(iSigma)
}

EPsi<-EPsi/s
ESigma<-ESigma/s

amprod<-function (A, M, k)
{
  K <- length(dim(A))
  AM <- M %*% mat(A, k)
  AMA <- array(AM, dim = c(dim(M)[1], dim(A)[-k]))
  aperm(AMA, match(1:K, c(k, (1:K)[-k])))
}

SPsi<-tcrossprod( mat( amprod(Y, mhalf(iSig), 2), 1) )
